# Canary scenario: a clean chat turn should pass exit 0. If this fails,
# the harness is broken; investigate before trusting the segfault scenario.
#
# Pacing notes (Phase 5 manual verification):
# - The 500ms idle BEFORE `send` lets zag's input handler fully wire up;
#   without it, send races startup and only the first byte lands.

spawn ./zig-out/bin/zag
wait_text /Welcome to zag/
wait_idle 500ms
send "hello" <Enter>
wait_idle 5s
snapshot final
